trans-unit.source: Provides methods that ASP.NET uses to invoke the application-preload feature in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Fornece métodos que utiliza o ASP.NET para invocar a funcionalidade da aplicação-pré-carregamento no [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Called by [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to notify ASP.NET whether an application should be preloaded.
trans-unit.target: Chamado pelo [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] notificar ASP.NET se uma aplicação deve ser pré-carregada.

trans-unit.source: The unique ID of the application.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate that the application should be preloaded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para indicar que a aplicação deve ser pré-carregado; caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Calls [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to get information that is required in order to preload an application.
trans-unit.target: Chamadas [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para obter informações que são necessárias para pré-carregar uma aplicação.

trans-unit.source: IIS calls ASP.NET through this interface, supplying a reference to an object that implements the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil> interface.
trans-unit.target: IIS chama ASP.NET através deste interface, fornecendo uma referência a um objeto que implementa o <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>interface.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET uses that interface later to perform a callback into IIS to get preload information for individual applications.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET utiliza essa interface posterior para efetuar uma chamada de retorno no IIS para obter informações de pré-carregamento para aplicações individuais.

trans-unit.source: The handle to an unmanaged interface in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that ASP.NET calls to get information.
trans-unit.target: O identificador de uma interface não gerido em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] que ASP.NET chama-se para obter informações.
